de.uzk.hki.da.cb

Class AbstractAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uzk.hki.da.cb.AbstractAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArchiveReplicationAction, ArchiveReplicationCheckAction, AuditAction, BuildAIPAction, CheckFormatsAction, CleanWorkAreaAction, ConvertAction, CreateEDMAction, CreatePremisAction, DeleteObjectAction, FetchPIPsAction, FriendshipConversionAction, IndexESAction, ObjectToWorkAreaAction, PostRetrievalAction, PrepareSendToPresenterAction, RegisterURNAction, RestartIngestWorkflowAction, RetrievalAction, ScanAction, ScanForPresentationAction, SendToPresenterAction, ShortenFileNamesAction, TarAction, UnpackAction, UpdateMetadataAction

    public abstract class AbstractAction
extends Object
implements Runnable
    Fetches Jobs with a given start state, but only when the local ContentBroker is the owner of the Job. The class makes heavy use of the template method pattern. Extension notes: In order to extend the BaseAction please follow a few instructions:
    1. Helper methods of extended classes which should be separetely tested should have default (package) visibility.
    2. Constructors which should only be seen by tests should also have default (package) visibility.
    Author:
    Daniel M. de Oliveira & the DA-NRW team
